Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:55.60,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}All wishes remain in my soul, Endlessly resound in my ears
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.14,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}倾尽我的全心 光芒引领方向
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.14,0:00:37.39,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}紧抱万千思绪 将其怀揣于心
